Package: scDesign2
Type: Package
Title: scDesign2: A statistical simulator for scRNA-seq data with gene correlation captured
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tianyi Sun
Maintainer: Tianyi Sun <tianyisun@ucla.edu>
Description: A flexible statistical simulator for scRNA-seq data that can generate data with
    gene correlation captured, and with varing number of cells and sequencing depth.
